Dialogue: 10,0:00:04.32,0:00:05.48,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:13.91,0:00:14.80,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:16.41,0:00:17.87,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Mary?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:25.36,0:00:28.01,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,What? You have a present for me?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:28.01,0:00:30.26,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:30.26,0:00:31.26,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,What are you giving me?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:35.31,0:00:36.56,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Wait, Mary!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:36.56,0:00:38.14,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Stop, stop, stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:38.14,0:00:40.64,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:47.65,0:00:52.36,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Men... Men are so...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:53.63,0:00:56.11,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Mary.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:56.11,0:00:58.32,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Just kidding!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:58.32,0:01:01.45,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Why would a young wolf like me be sorry?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:01.45,0:01:03.76,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,I wanna see the rest, the rest...{loli hentai!!!}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:03.76,0:01:05.58,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Wait! There's no time for that!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:12.84,0:01:14.97,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,I definitely can't be late today.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:45.83,0:02:46.64,Default,MASAKI,0,0,0,,Finished.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:47.17,0:02:50.02,Default,MASAKI,0,0,0,,I managed to finish in time.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:51.73,0:02:55.02,Default,MASAKI,0,0,0,,I hope Shun-chan likes them.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:59.37,0:03:00.95,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,Kaname-kun...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:00.95,0:03:02.78,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:05.33,0:03:08.83,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,This guy's already had some chocolate, and it's still so early!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:08.83,0:03:12.04,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,Shut up! It was from my mom.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:12.04,0:03:14.29,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,I'll eat it when I get home.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:14.29,0:03:17.25,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,Let go. Seriously, I'll be late to school.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:17.25,0:03:19.80,Default,MOM,0,0,0,,So what? I'm being serious, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.80,0:03:21.20,Default,MOM,0,0,0,,{\i1}Really{\i0} serious.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.20,0:03:22.97,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,You're only making it harder for me to eat it!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:23.64,0:03:28.00,Default,MOM,0,0,0,,Fine. I guess I should just throw it in the trash, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.00,0:03:30.40,Default,MOM,0,0,0,,Sorry for giving you so much trouble this morning.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:30.40,0:03:34.40,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,The way you pout like that is what gives me the most trouble!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:34.40,0:03:35.57,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,Fine, whatever!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.62,0:03:44.74,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,Okay, it's delicious.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:44.74,0:03:46.12,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,I'm off.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:47.20,0:03:49.20,Default,MOM,0,0,0,,Kaname-kun.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.72,0:03:51.75,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.75,0:03:54.35,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,Who cares about Valentine's Day, anyway?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.35,0:03:55.76,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,It's cute...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:55.76,0:03:59.63,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Going overboard for the people you love.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.63,0:04:01.00,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.00,0:04:05.27,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,If you can't understand women, you'll always be a child.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.27,0:04:07.64,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,I {\i1}am{\i0} her child.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.64,0:04:09.68,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,Stop acting like we're lovers.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:09.68,0:04:11.19,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:11.19,0:04:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's Valentine's Day, isn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:14.02,0:04:17.67,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,Why don't we all have some chocolate at lunch break?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.67,0:04:19.73,Default,YUTA,0,0,0,,Shun, when did you become a teenage girl?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.73,0:04:20.32,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:20.32,0:04:22.61,Default,GIRL 1,0,0,0,,Azuma-sensei, have this.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:22.61,0:04:23.94,Default,GIRL 1,0,0,0,,I'm serious, don't ya know?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.94,0:04:25.58,Default,AZUMA,0,0,0,,Th-Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:25.58,0:04:28.03,Default,GIRL 2,0,0,0,,Man, what are you saying?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.03,0:04:30.45,Default,GIRL 1,0,0,0,,See you later, Sensei.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:30.45,0:04:34.58,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Azuma-sensei, you're so lucky!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.58,0:04:37.94,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,How can you have so much already while we have none?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.94,0:04:40.88,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,They say teachers are always role models for their students.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.88,0:04:42.21,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Way to go.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.21,0:04:46.84,Default,AZUMA,0,0,0,,But these chocolates don't really mean much. NThey're just to show appreciation for my work.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:46.84,0:04:49.73,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,There you go again. You're always so modest.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.73,0:04:51.47,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,You sure did get a lot.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:51.47,0:04:54.16,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,Can you eat all of those by yourself?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.16,0:04:57.48,Default,AZUMA,0,0,0,,Yes. I'm happy to receive them, so I'll eat them all.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.48,0:04:59.81,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,You'll eat every last morsel, and leave no one behind? {this pun makes no sense}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.81,0:05:01.47,Default,AZUMA,0,0,0,,And leave {\i1}not one{\i0} behind.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:01.47,0:05:04.86,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah. Whatever you say.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.60,0:05:07.52,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,{\i1}Today is Valentine's Day.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:07.52,0:05:09.33,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,{\i1}A day for boys and girls to pretend
Dialogue: 10,0:05:09.33,0:05:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that they don't notice how nervous everyone else is feeling...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.83,0:05:14.33,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Pretend"?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.33,0:05:18.17,Default,TAKAHASHI,0,0,0,,There he is.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.34,0:05:23.67,Default,TAKAHASHI,0,0,0,,Matsuoka-kun, Yuuta-kun.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:24.96,0:05:26.55,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,Takahashi-san?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:27.46,0:05:30.47,Default,TAKAHASHI,0,0,0,,All the girls in class got together and made some chocolate.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.47,0:05:32.18,Default,TAKAHASHI,0,0,0,,It's not much, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.18,0:05:34.81,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.43,0:05:36.31,Default,YUTA,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:40.06,0:05:45.03,Default,TAKAHASHI,0,0,0,,Well, that's... every... thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:45.03,0:05:48.45,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,Oh, yes. Thank you for specially giving us some.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.09,0:05:56.21,Default,YUTA,0,0,0,,No, everyone got a pack.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:58.21,0:06:00.79,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Everyone's going on about chocolate this,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:00.79,0:06:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and chocolate that, and chocolate chococochoco!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.71,0:06:04.02,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,You can't even say it anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.02,0:06:04.92,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,I don't care!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.07,0:06:09.35,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,A bitter man ignores events like this
Dialogue: 10,0:06:09.35,0:06:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and focuses on his studies.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.97,0:06:14.10,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Right, Yukki?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.60,0:06:18.36,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Huh? Someone decorated my pencil case.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:19.15,0:06:21.56,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Like hell they did!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:22.03,0:06:26.13,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Yukki, you got a ton of chocolate, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.13,0:06:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.53,0:06:27.57,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ow, ow.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.32,0:06:33.58,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Lucky guy. I want some chocolate, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.08,0:06:38.16,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,I wonder if Mary's gonna give Shun-chan chocolate.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.87,0:06:42.63,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,{\i1}But maybe... just maybe...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:42.63,0:06:45.84,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe she'll give me some, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:45.84,0:06:50.34,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe the dream I had this morning was a premonition or something...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.60,0:07:03.86,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,H-Hey, Mary-san.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.86,0:07:07.69,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,What's up? You seem really tired.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.69,0:07:13.91,Default,MASAKI,0,0,0,,Yeah. I've been practicing making truffles every night.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:13.91,0:07:16.24,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,Masaki-chan, have you not been getting enough sleep?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:16.24,0:07:17.79,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:17.79,0:07:21.25,Default,MASAKI,0,0,0,,No, I'm just super duper!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:23.21,0:07:24.59,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.13,0:07:29.05,Default,MASAKI,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:36.72,0:07:39.25,Default,YUTA,0,0,0,,Yes, yes. What is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.25,0:07:44.23,Default,MASAKI,0,0,0,,Well, uh... um...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.23,0:07:51.77,Default,MASAKI,0,0,0,,Do you think Shun-chan likes... s-sweet things?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.98,0:07:54.93,Default,YUTA,0,0,0,,Yeah, he does.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.20,0:07:58.66,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,I wonder what's wrong...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.83,0:08:02.54,Default,YUTA,0,0,0,,Anything else? Are you all set?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.25,0:08:04.83,Default,MASAKI,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:13.68,0:08:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:21.64,0:08:24.40,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,Kaname-kun, you seem down.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:24.40,0:08:27.52,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,I was just thinking about how my mom's going to force me to eat
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.52,0:08:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,all that chocolate cake she made when I get home.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:30.39,0:08:32.58,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,Just thinking about it gives me heartburn.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.58,0:08:36.91,Default,YUTA,0,0,0,,Kaname, since you're an only child, you get all of the love your mother has to offer.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.91,0:08:38.92,Default,YUTA,0,0,0,,It would be different if you had a younger brother.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.92,0:08:41.91,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Why don't you tell your mom you want a kid?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.91,0:08:42.75,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,Like hell I will!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:42.75,0:08:44.98,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,That means something completely different!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.98,0:08:47.92,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,D-Did you get any chocolate today, Shun-chan?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:47.92,0:08:50.61,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,What? I never get any.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:50.61,0:08:55.43,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,My mother or sister just give me some every year.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:56.84,0:08:58.18,Default,STUDENT A,0,0,0,,U-Um, excuse me.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:04.02,0:09:06.20,Default,STUDENT A,0,0,0,,I-It's a chocolate tart.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.20,0:09:09.02,Default,STUDENT A,0,0,0,,I made it myself, so it's not very...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.02,0:09:12.90,Default,STUDENT A,0,0,0,,I'm sure it's not any good, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:14.03,0:09:15.91,Default,STUDENT A,0,0,0,,W-Well, um... If you're not...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:16.90,0:09:20.74,Default,STUDENT A,0,0,0,,dating anyone right now...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.67,0:09:35.42,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,No, no. This is, u-um...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.42,0:09:37.73,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,What? Come on.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.73,0:09:38.68,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Don't hide it.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.68,0:09:40.77,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,She was from another school, wasn't she?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:40.77,0:09:43.07,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Way to go, Shun. She was all over you.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.07,0:09:46.35,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,N-No, that's not it. Please stop.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:46.35,0:09:47.68,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Show us what's inside.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.68,0:09:49.10,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,H-Hey, wait.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:49.10,0:09:52.52,Default,YUTA,0,0,0,,Good for you. Does it really bother you that much?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.52,0:09:54.69,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,Huh? Well, I...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:55.64,0:09:57.20,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,I'm happy, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.90,0:10:00.99,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Wow. It's a homemade tart.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.99,0:10:02.70,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,It looks delicious.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.70,0:10:06.20,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,Hey, don't open it!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:07.60,0:10:08.25,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Mary.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:15.07,0:10:16.47,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Mary!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:16.47,0:10:17.93,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Mary!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:18.89,0:10:20.05,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Ma—
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.05,0:10:21.18,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:21.18,0:10:23.68,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:23.68,0:10:25.22,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Is that what I think it is?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.22,0:10:26.18,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Aren't those for Shun—
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.18,0:10:28.48,Default,MASAKI,0,0,0,,You try one!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.65,0:10:31.52,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,What do you think you're—
Dialogue: 10,0:10:30.94,0:10:31.52,Default,MASAKI,0,0,0,,{\an8}See?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.52,0:10:33.36,Default,MASAKI,0,0,0,,They taste weird, don't they?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.36,0:10:34.53,Default,MASAKI,0,0,0,,They don't taste any good, do they?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.37,0:10:37.57,Default,MASAKI,0,0,0,,I know! I'll buy something from the convenience store, and...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:37.57,0:10:39.03,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Hey, wait! Wait—
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.03,0:10:40.03,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.99,0:10:44.16,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Mary!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:44.16,0:10:47.66,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,A-Are you okay, Mary? Mary!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:47.66,0:10:51.17,Default,SOCCER,0,0,0,,Excuse me. Can you return our ball, please?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.13,0:11:00.01,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Hold on, Mary!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.01,0:11:01.93,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Don't die on me!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.90,0:11:07.02,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,L-Lack of sleep?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:07.02,0:11:09.50,Default,NURSE,0,0,0,,She doesn't have a fever.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:09.50,0:11:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll be fine once she gets some rest.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:14.36,0:11:15.27,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:16.13,0:11:19.79,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Why'd you have to fall over so dramatically?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:20.74,0:11:23.70,Default,NURSE,0,0,0,,I have to step out for a minute.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:23.70,0:11:27.70,Default,NURSE,0,0,0,,Can you walk Satou-san home if she wakes up?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.70,0:11:29.56,Default,NURSE,0,0,0,,I'm a little worried about her.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.56,0:11:30.92,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Ah, sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:30.92,0:11:33.38,Default,NURSE,0,0,0,,She doesn't even have a test coming up.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:33.38,0:11:36.80,Default,NURSE,0,0,0,,I wonder what she was working so hard on...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.97,0:12:27.30,Default,MASAKI,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh? Where am I?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:27.30,0:12:30.18,Default,MASAKI,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait, when did I fall asleep?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.97,0:12:32.26,Default,MASAKI,0,0,0,,{\i1}Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:36.99,0:12:38.77,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Mary, are you sure you can...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.77,0:12:40.03,Default,MASAKI,0,0,0,,What time is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.33,0:12:43.53,Default,MASAKI,0,0,0,,What am I going to do? I didn't give Shun-chan any chocolate.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.20,0:12:47.78,Default,MASAKI,0,0,0,,I need to go to the convenience store and buy some...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.93,0:12:52.04,Default,MASAKI,0,0,0,,No, Shun-chan must have gone home already.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.42,0:12:55.04,Default,MASAKI,0,0,0,,It's over.{shut up mary, no one cares}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:00.13,0:13:01.27,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:01.27,0:13:02.55,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,[hard to read?],Even if you can't give him anything today,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.55,0:13:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,you can still give him something tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.38,0:13:05.68,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.68,0:13:08.57,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,You should have given him the chocolate you made.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.57,0:13:09.96,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,They were good.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.53,0:13:11.97,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Hey, Mary.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:16.44,0:13:18.15,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Come on, Mary...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.40,0:13:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{I really don't understand this beach bs}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.42,0:13:44.30,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey, did you really give that teacher some chocolate?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.30,0:13:47.13,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,{\an8}I was so nervous.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:47.13,0:13:48.43,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,{\an8}You did it?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:48.43,0:13:49.85,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.61,0:14:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{lmao that face tho}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.19,0:14:08.36,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,{\i1}What am I doing?! What am I doing?! What am I doing?!{being a loli pedo obviously}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.80,0:14:32.01,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,I'm impressed you can eat so many sweets.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:32.45,0:14:35.47,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,Haven't you been eating all of that chocolate you got yesterday?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:35.47,0:14:37.10,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,Mm, yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.10,0:14:38.81,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,Mm?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:38.81,0:14:41.77,Default,YUTA,0,0,0,,Yuuki, you'd better give them some on White Day in return.{white day is the opposite where boys give chocolate instead of girls. should this be a note at the top? meh}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:42.27,0:14:44.53,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,I don't think I'll have any left by then.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:45.08,0:14:46.67,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,Not those.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.60,0:14:50.16,Default,YUTA,0,0,0,,Shun, Chizuru, do you guys want some...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:51.35,0:14:53.63,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,What's wrong with them?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:53.63,0:14:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,They've been like that since this morning.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.49,0:14:56.75,Default,YUTA,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:56.75,0:14:59.04,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wanna die.{every millennial ever}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:59.04,0:15:01.85,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why did I do that yesterday?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:01.85,0:15:04.34,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,{\i1}What am I going to do when I see her again?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:04.34,0:15:09.26,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, but Mary's body was so soft.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.26,0:15:11.18,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, I shouldn't think about that.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.81,0:15:13.72,Default,YUTA,0,0,0,,Oh, looks like Chizuru's fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.72,0:15:15.76,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,He's obviously not!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:16.88,0:15:17.81,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Shun.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.35,0:15:19.27,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Shun.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:20.55,0:15:21.74,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.74,0:15:24.32,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,What happened after that girl
Dialogue: 10,0:15:24.32,0:15:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,confessed her feelings to you yesterday?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:26.48,0:15:29.28,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Her cell number was on the card, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:29.28,0:15:33.20,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,Oh, um... I haven't...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.57,0:15:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,messaged her yet.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:36.20,0:15:37.94,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,You haven't?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.94,0:15:39.42,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,She doesn't go to our school.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.42,0:15:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't text her, she...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.09,0:15:43.04,Default,YUTA,0,0,0,,That girl was pretty amazing.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:43.54,0:15:46.91,Default,YUTA,0,0,0,,It's not easy going to another school by yourself.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:48.05,0:15:49.84,Default,STUDENT A,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.38,0:15:53.00,Default,STUDENT A,0,0,0,,I guess you don't know what to do when a stranger
Dialogue: 10,0:15:53.00,0:15:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,suddenly hands you chocolate.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.96,0:15:58.39,Default,STUDENT A,0,0,0,,But we cross paths most mornings.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.39,0:16:03.14,Default,STUDENT A,0,0,0,,You even picked up my train pass for me once.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:05.81,0:16:11.65,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,U-Um, I have things to do, so I... I'm going home.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.53,0:16:13.39,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,Oh. Sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:15.88,0:16:18.40,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,Is he going to be okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.40,0:16:21.75,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,It's probably the first time anyone's confessed their feelings to Shun before.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.63,0:16:25.29,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,I bet he doesn't know what to do.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.95,0:16:27.50,Default,YUTA,0,0,0,,You're probably right.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.50,0:16:31.01,Default,YUTA,0,0,0,,He's been standing there all day just thinking.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:31.01,0:16:33.80,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "probably"?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:33.80,0:16:36.76,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,You should be helping him with his problem or something.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.47,0:16:41.77,Default,YUTA,0,0,0,,Shun prefers to think for\Nhimself when he has a decision to make.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:42.35,0:16:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow...{oh shun...}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:47.06,0:16:48.48,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:49.14,0:16:50.36,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:51.04,0:16:52.11,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.61,0:16:55.28,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,I was convinced something was wrong.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:55.76,0:16:57.07,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,"Something"?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.28,0:17:01.29,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,With your beloved Mary-chan.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:01.29,0:17:03.21,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,What? How did you know?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:03.96,0:17:07.75,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,How? I can tell by looking at you.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.25,0:17:11.21,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,{\an8}So what happened?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.21,0:17:13.14,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,{\an8}Nothing.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:12.44,0:17:14.72,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,What are they doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.14,0:17:14.72,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,{\an8}Nothing happened!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:14.72,0:17:16.84,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Come on. Why don't you tell Big Brother Yuuki?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.84,0:17:18.26,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Come on, come on, come on.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.84,0:17:18.26,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,{\an8}Cut it out, Yukki.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:18.85,0:17:21.27,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Yukki, you'd better not fall in love with her, too.{how could anyone}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:21.70,0:17:23.52,Default,YUTA,0,0,0,,Chizuru, where are you going?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:23.52,0:17:25.03,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,I'm going home!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:25.03,0:17:26.60,Default,KANAME,0,0,0,,What's his problem?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:27.52,0:17:29.52,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,I won't.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:49.33,0:17:50.79,Default,MASAKI,0,0,0,,Shun-chan.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.29,0:18:00.40,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shun-chan doesn't live in this direction.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:00.40,0:18:02.98,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where's he going?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:02.98,0:18:06.27,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sorry, Shun-chan.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.27,0:18:10.34,Default,STUDENT B,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.34,0:18:12.02,Default,STUDENT C,0,0,0,,Isn't he from another school?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.72,0:18:17.15,Default,STUDENT A,0,0,0,,Um, is something wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:20.03,0:18:23.94,Default,STUDENT A,0,0,0,,I was so surprised to see you standing at the gates.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:23.94,0:18:26.58,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,S-Sorry for showing up unannounced.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:26.58,0:18:29.54,Default,STUDENT A,0,0,0,,Oh, no. That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.21,0:18:33.05,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,Um, well...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.13,0:18:35.79,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wh-What am I going to do?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:35.79,0:18:37.89,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,{\i1}Something big is going down.{more like an awkward moment going down}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:37.89,0:18:39.55,Default,MASAKI,0,0,0,,What are you up to?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:40.22,0:18:41.48,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Mary!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:41.48,0:18:43.26,Default,MASAKI,0,0,0,,Shun-chan isn't with you?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.81,0:18:50.35,Default,MASAKI,0,0,0,,You're {\i1}spying{\i0} on him? I can't believe you!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:52.30,0:18:54.98,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,I get it, so pipe down.{just hug her again; that'll shut her up lul}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.98,0:18:56.49,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:56.49,0:18:58.99,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,I can't go out with you.{who tf dates a person they don't know anyway}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:00.00,0:19:00.99,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:05.24,0:19:07.00,Default,STUDENT A,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:07.39,0:19:09.50,Default,STUDENT A,0,0,0,,Oh, it's fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:09.50,0:19:16.00,Default,STUDENT A,0,0,0,,Um, I didn't really think it would work out, so I...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:16.55,0:19:18.35,Default,STUDENT A,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I guess.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:18.35,0:19:20.28,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,But I was happy.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.89,0:19:23.01,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,I was really happy.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:24.55,0:19:27.52,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,The chocolate tart was delicious.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:28.14,0:19:29.31,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:34.23,0:19:39.40,Default,STUDENT A,0,0,0,,I'm happy you came all the way to my school to meet me.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:58.08,0:19:59.46,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,You okay with this?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:59.46,0:20:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I guess that's not what I really mean, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:06.22,0:20:08.89,Default,MASAKI,0,0,0,,Shun-chan was always so nice.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:12.89,0:20:17.07,Default,MASAKI,0,0,0,,I always believed he would happily accept how I feel.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:17.94,0:20:22.86,Default,MASAKI,0,0,0,,{\i1}I thought every day after that would be so fun and full of happiness...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.86,0:20:24.11,Default,MASAKI,0,0,0,,{\i1}But for the first time,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.12,0:20:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I began to think he might not accept my feelings, after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.76,0:20:34.17,Default,MASAKI,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was so afraid and uncertain...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.17,0:20:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that I couldn't work up the courage to do it.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:36.08,0:20:37.59,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was delicious.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:38.30,0:20:39.59,Default,SHUN,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:39.59,0:20:42.47,Default,MASAKI,0,0,0,,{\i1}I couldn't do it.
