Dialogue: 10,0:21:09.99,0:21:11.63,Default,MASAKI,0,0,0,,"Eye"? What are you...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:11.63,0:21:14.62,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Huh? You've never made an eye shape before?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:14.62,0:21:17.63,Default,MASAKI,0,0,0,,Sure. In elementary school.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:17.63,0:21:18.90,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,I'm the left eye.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.90,0:21:21.46,Default,MASAKI,0,0,0,,Huh? Then, I'm...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.46,0:21:22.63,Default,MASAKI,0,0,0,,the right eye?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:23.71,0:21:26.58,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,You're way too short for this.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:26.58,0:21:28.05,Default,MASAKI,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:28.05,0:21:31.14,Default,MASAKI,0,0,0,,I only did it because you did!{monkey see, monkey do}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:36.39,0:21:40.15,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,{\i1}My evening with you unfolds before my eyes.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:41.57,0:21:45.54,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,{\i1}Blindingly bright and overwhelmingly happy.{so this random shit is supposed to show his feelings?}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:45.54,0:21:47.66,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,{\i1}And somewhere deep inside, really frustrated.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:49.54,0:21:50.99,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,I like you, Mary.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:03.05,0:22:05.04,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Huh? Wait, Mary-san...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:05.04,0:22:06.76,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,Are you mad?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:07.82,0:22:10.93,Default,MASAKI,0,0,0,,Why did you have to say that?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:10.93,0:22:12.94,Default,MASAKI,0,0,0,,I mean, you're {\i1}you{\i0}.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:12.94,0:22:13.93,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:24.94,0:22:26.15,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:27.02,0:22:28.63,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,{\i1}So happy that I could gush tears.{like gushers? I haven't had those in ages...why am I writing random shit in these subs?no one is gonna read them anyways lmaothis is how I make timing/qcing interestingdon't hatemasturbate!okokok I'm done}
Dialogue: 10,0:22:29.99,0:22:31.80,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,{\i1}So happy that I could overflow with smiles.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:33.34,0:22:36.12,Default,CHIZURU,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm happy that I love you.
